French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That was also met with relatively low winds, something that would wreak havoc on the men's skiff medal race at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 912, \"to\": 1036, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The first attempt to hold the race was abandoned inside a few minutes, with it becoming clear that there was not sufficient winds in order to hold a fair competition.\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1204, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\ud83d\\udea8 EN DIRECTO \\ud83d\\udea8Diego Bot\\u00edn y Florian Trittel, a por la medalla en la Medal Race que acaba de arrancar.\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1307, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1222, \"end\": 1227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego_Columbus\", \"score\": 0.9972734191344106, \"rank\": 0.0027340350941293615, \"text\": \"Diego\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego_Columbus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego_Columbus\"}, {\"begin\": 1228, \"end\": 1233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jaime_Bot\\u00edn\", \"score\": 0.876375122017715, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bot\\u00edn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jaime_Bot\\u00edn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jaime_Bot\\u00edn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Marchan l\\u00edderes en la generalS\\u00edguela en@streammaxespic.twitter.com/L6lPEklzkC  - Eurosport.es (@Eurosport_ES)August 1, 2024    Ireland were probably delighted with that move, considering that they sat in eighth place at the time.\", \"from\": 1308, \"to\": 1537, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1437, \"end\": 1444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.999406450861411, \"rank\": 0.0005930374597241221, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ire